\c 18  
\cl Dwom 18 
\d \nd Awurade\nd* akoa Dawid dwom. ∆Ütoo saa dwom yi maa \nd Awurade\nd*, bere a ogyee no fii n ºatamfo nyinaa ne Saulo nsam no. 
\q1  
\v 1 Med…î wo, \nd Awurade\nd*, m ºaho…îden. 
