\v 8 Bra b…õhw…õ \nd Awurade\nd* nnwuma, 
\q2 …îs…õe a …îde aba asase no so. 
\q1  
\v 9 ∆Üma akodi gyae kosi asase ano. 
\q2 Obubu agyan mu na …îs…õe peaw; 
\q2 …îde ogya hyew nkatabo. 
\q1  
\v 10 Mony…õ komm na munhu s…õ me ne Onyankop…în; 
\q2 w…îb…õma me so w…î amanaman no mu, 
