\q1  
\v 22 ‚ÄúMunnwen eyi ho, mo a mo wer…õ fi Onyankop…în, 
\q2 any…õ saa a, m…õtetew mo mu nketenkete a obiara remmegye mo; 
\q1  
\v 23 Nea …îb…î aseda af…îre no hy…õ me anuonyam, 
